---
// TerminalTmux.astro
---

<div class="terminal">
  <div class="terminal-header">
    <span class="terminal-button red"></span>
    <span class="terminal-button yellow"></span>
    <span class="terminal-button green"></span>
    <span class="terminal-title">tmux - portfolio</span>
  </div>
  <div class="terminal-body">
    <pre><code>$ tmux new -s portfolio

[0] 0:crow@portfolio* "zsh" 01:23 12-Dec-25

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                             │
│  Welcome back to Crow's Portfolio Terminal                                  │
│                                                                             │
│  Available commands:                                                        │
│  - ls: List pages                                                           │
│  - cd <page>: Navigate to page                                              │
│  - help: Show help                                                          │
│  - exit: Close session                                                      │
│                                                                             │
│  Type 'ls' to see available pages.                                          │
│                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

$ <span class="cursor">_</span></span></code></pre>
  </div>
</div>



<style>
   .terminal {
     max-width: 100%;
     margin: 2rem auto;
     background: var(--bg);
     border: 1px solid var(--border);
     border-radius: 8px;
     font-family: 'Iosevka', monospace;
     box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
   }

  .terminal-header {
    background: var(--bg-soft);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
  }

  .terminal-button {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .green { background: #28ca42; }

  .terminal-title {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 1rem;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .terminal-body pre {
    margin: 0;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  .terminal-body code {
    background: transparent;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .terminal-body strong {
    color: var(--yellow);
  }

  .terminal-body .green {
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .terminal-body .blue {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .terminal-body .yellow {
    color: var(--yellow);
  }

  .terminal-body .red {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .terminal-body a {
    color: var(--aqua);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .terminal-body a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .terminal-body a {
    color: var(--blue);
  }



  /* Responsive */


  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .terminal {
      margin: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .terminal-header {
      padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .terminal-body {
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }

    .terminal-title {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>